            <div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none text-ide-text-muted leading-relaxed">
                <p>EchoJournal was constructed as part of the <em>Pl Mobile Dev Campus</em> community challenge. It goes beyond simple audio recording by allowing users to construct a rich, filterable timeline composed of their voice logs, tagged heavily with metadata layers indicating varying mood states and semantic topics, potentially backed by AI transcription.</p>
